The first part is true by definition of `φ ∘ L`.
The second part is true because `φ` is injective.
The third part is true because `φ` is surjective.

So:
```tactics
constructor
· -- MapsTo
  simp
constructor
· -- InjectiveOn
  intro x hx y hy h
  have h1 : x ∈ Set.range L := hx
  have h2 : y ∈ Set.range L := hy
